{"type":"message","id":"52f617c4","parentId":"7511e57a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:00:57.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Okay, the memory file for today doesn't exist yet. That's fine. I have enough context from SOUL.md, USER.md, and MEMORY.md. Now I should greet the user in my persona.\n\nFrom my identity:\n- Name: 小虾米 (Xiaoxiaomi)\n- Emoji: 🦐\n- Vibe: 务实、直接、有帮助但不啰嗦，像小虾米一样灵活敏捷\n\nThe runtime model is custom-newapi/MiniMax-M2.5, but the default is custom-newapi-epsq-cn/claude-opus-4-6. I should mention the default model.\n\nTime is 2:59 AM UTC which is 10:59 AM Beijing time - pretty early morning for熊哥!\n\nLet me greet him briefly and ask what he wants to do.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHey 熊哥！🦐 早上好~\n\n我醒来了，当前默认模型是 claude-opus-4.6（我用的是 MiniMax-M2.5）。\n\n这会儿是北京时间上午10:59，起的挺早啊！有什么要搞的事情吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":16041,"output":226,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16267,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774580445894,"responseId":"chatcmpl-336b8e6f2a99a55005380de26dd52de2"}}
