{"type":"message","id":"70a25856","parentId":"f91c0207","timestamp":"2026-03-27T03:12:25.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！在 `session-management-compaction.md` 文档里有 `reserveTokens: 16384`。\n\n16k = 16,384 是 OpenClaw 的**默认保留token数**，用于压缩会话时保留的空间。这是源代码中的硬编码默认值。\n\n让我给熊哥解释一下：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！16k (16,384) 是 OpenClaw 源代码中的**默认值**，定义在会话压缩策略中：\n\n**文件：** `docs/reference/session-management-compaction.md:239`\n```javascript\nreserveTokens: 16384,\n```\n\n这是**硬编码的默认值**，表示每次压缩会话时保留给系统/工具的空间。如果想修改：\n\n1. **运行时调整** - 使用命令：`/context reserve <数量>`\n2. **配置文件** - 可以在 `config.json` 中设置会话级配置\n\n不过通常 16k 足够用，95% 只是说明当前对话历史较长，不是问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-newapi","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":16369,"output":194,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16563,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774581142439,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7053758ffd1096099d8a1dfe6567c16f"}}
